“Balada de Mulán”.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":347} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://stageonemag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/image005.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-347\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Mulán </em></strong>se estrenará en cines en marzo de 2020.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Mulán, la guerrera china','','publish','open','open','','mulan-la-guerrera-china','','','2019-07-10 20:33:06','2019-07-10 18:33:06','',0,'http://stageonemag.com/?p=346',0,'post','',0),(347,2,'2019-07-10 20:27:53','2019-07-10 18:27:53','','image005','','inherit','open','closed','','image005-2','','','2019-07-10 20:27:53','2019-07-10 18:27:53','',346,'http://stageonemag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/image005.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(348,2,'2019-07-10 20:28:09','2019-07-10 18:28:09','','null','Disney\'s MULAN..Mulan (Yifei Liu)..Photo: Film Frame..© 2019 Disney Enterprises, Inc. All Rights Reserved.','inherit','open','closed','','null-5','','','2019-07-10 20:28:09','2019-07-10 18:28:09','',346,'http://stageonemag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mulán_imagen.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(349,2,'2019-07-10 20:28:23','2019-07-10 18:28:23','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>La aclamada cineasta Niki Caro le da vida al épico relato de la legendaria guerrera china en la nueva películade Disney, <strong><em>M</em>ulán</strong>, en la que una joven valiente arriesga todo, por amor a su familia y a su país, para convertirse en una de las más grandes guerreras que China haya conocido.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":348,\"width\":512,\"height\":242} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"http://stageonemag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Mulán_imagen-1024x484.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-348\" width=\"512\" height=\"242\"/><figcaption>Disney\'s MULAN..Mulan (Yifei Liu)..Photo: Film Frame..© 2019 Disney Enterprises, Inc. All Rights Reserved.</figca